Functions in the disk API. These functions are for interacting with disk drives:
disk.isPresent( side )
disk.setLabel( side, label )
disk.getLabel( side )
disk.hasData( side )
disk.getMountPath( side )
disk.hasAudio( side )
disk.getAudioTitle( side )
disk.playAudio( side )
disk.stopAudio( )
disk.eject( side )
disk.getID( side )

Events fired by the disk API:
"disk" when a disk or other item is inserted into a disk drive. Argument is the side
"disk_eject" when a disk is removed from a disk drive. Argument is the side
Type "help events" to learn about the event system.